snippet.title: Board Battlefield - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Board Battlefield is now available on Google Play:

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.UnwrittenRules.BoardBattlefield

Board Battlefield is a simple turn based strategy game offering a unique mix of tactics and luck.
